text: Renata Bianchi (12 July 1926 - 1966) was an Italian gymnast. She competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:1966 deaths Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Genoa
